  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, partial assessment)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set at 3. Ten of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed; three factors — Model form, Model inputs, and Equivalency of input parameters — are recorded as not-assessed on the basis that their evaluation was deemed beyond the scope of the current submission cycle. No concrete justification for deferral is provided. The package is submitted as Accepted despite the unassessed factors at MRL 3, which materially weakens credibility evidence.",
