      "acceptanceCriteria": "At least three independent experimental replicates per operating point to characterize biological variability in hemolysis measurements.",
      "rationale": "Only two replicates were available for operating points 3 and 5 due to sample attrition. Biological variability is undercharacterized at those conditions. Achieved level 2."
